This project provides a Discord meme bot template.

## What it does
- Posts a random meme to your configured channel at your configured interval.
- Lets users request a meme instantly with `meme!now`.
- Supports token configuration with either `config.py` (`TOKEN`) or the `DISCORD_TOKEN` environment variable.

## Setup
1. Update `config.py` with your server/channel details and preferred interval.
2. Add your bot token to `TOKEN` in `config.py` (or set `DISCORD_TOKEN`).
3. Install dependencies and run:
   - `pip install discord requests`
   - `python3 main.py`

If you use a custom meme API endpoint, make sure it returns JSON with an image URL field called `image` or `url`.
